column23: description

Finally, what you have been looking for in the heart of Annandale.   Welcome to this gorgeous 3 level colonial home with an attached 2 car garage.  It features 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 1/2 modernized bathrooms, lovely hardwood floors, and an updated U-shaped kitchen with a brand new stove. The backyard is an oasis of tranquility offering a huge deck right off kitchen, beautifully designed brick patio where you can enjoy a water fountain and nature. The landscape has been nicely maintained and filled with flowers and plants throughout, including an irrigation system.  The basement offers a kitchenette with freshly cleaned carpet and 2 bonus rooms.  It also includes a generator in case it is needed.  The entire property is great for entertainment.  It is close to I495, Gallows Rd., Rt50, I66, 5 minutes to Fairfax hospital, 10 minutes to Tysons Corner, and about 30 minutes to DC. There are many shops and restaurants in the nearby vicinity.  This property has everything you have been looking for and more!  Open house Saturday September 16th from 1-3pm and Sunday September 17th from 1-3pm.

Situated in the quiet Americana Fairfax neighborhood of Annandale, this townhouse is more than just a place to live – it's a place to call home. This space has been carefully updated and refreshed. The new appliances in the kitchen make meal prep a breeze, and the fresh carpeting throughout provides a cozy feel to each room. Modern lighting and a fresh coat of white paint brighten up the entire house. On the main level, the honey-colored wood floors lead you through the spacious dining room and into the open kitchen. From here, you can gaze out at the lovely landscaped backyard. Upstairs, the primary bedroom has been revamped with a newly renovated ensuite bathroom, complete with new cabinets, fixtures, and lighting. This level also includes two more bedrooms and another updated hall bathroom, ensuring ample space for everyone. Downstairs, the large open space is perfect for movie nights, especially with its charming fireplace. The big windows mean it's always light and inviting. When you step outside, the large fenced backyard stands ready for BBQs, relaxation, or play. It’s an outdoor green space that's all yours. Beyond the house itself, the community offers perks like a swimming pool, a playground for kids, and open green areas to relax or play. Plus, its convenient location means shopping, eating out, or commuting is easy and stress-free. If you're looking for a home that mixes comfort with practicality, this townhouse is definitely worth taking a tour.

Build the home of your dreams in the beautiful Annandale community of Wilburdale. The neighborhood feature flat lots mostly on half acres. This home sits on a flat lot on half an acre. Perfect lot for an investor or builder. There is a house currently on the property. Enter at your own risk. Home is currently not habitable. Major rehab or tear down and build a new home. Comps for larger homes are over $1.2 million. Survey is available in documents. Please schedule online. There is no lockbox.

Rarely available top level unit with vaulted ceilings and lots of natural light throughout. Renovated in 2021 with lots of upgrades and an open concept floor plan. LVP flooring through out, quarts countertops and spacious island offer lots of counter space and freshly painted. Exposed beams and high vaulted ceiling that go from 9 feet to 10.5 feet at their highest level. Great location close to lots of restaurants and grocery stores and low maintenance living. Easy access to 495, only 12 minutes from Mosaic district and Tysons Corner.

Don't miss this opportunity to own a truly exceptional property that combines elegant indoor living with the joys of outdoor recreation. Whether you're seeking a serene oasis for your family or an entertainer's paradise; this house with a sparkling swimming pool is a rare find that offers the best of both worlds. Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite residence offers the epitome of comfort and  luxurious living; nestled in a desirable neighborhood, ultimate retreat for families and those who appreciate the finer things in life. This generously sized home boasts spacious living areas, including a welcoming foyer, a light-filled living room, and a cozy family room with a fireplace, all of which provide ample space for relaxation and gatherings. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring high-end appliances, granite counter-tops, a center island, 42" upgraded cabinets with plenty of storage space. It's a culinary haven for preparing meals to enjoy with family and friends. The house offers a desirable layout with multiple bedrooms, including a lavish master suite with an en-suite bathroom and direct access to king size deck. Additional bedrooms are well-appointed and ideal for family members or guests.  Upgrades are included but not limited to recess lights, hardwood floors, designer bathrooms. For those who work from home, a dedicated home office space with built-in shelving and ample natural light is available, providing a quiet and productive workspace. The highlight of this property is its outdoor oasis, featuring a heated swimming pool surrounded by a beautifully landscaped yard. Whether you're taking a refreshing dip, sunbathing on the deck, or hosting summer BBQs, this space is designed for relaxation and entertainment. Huge patio adjacent to the pool area offers a shaded retreat for outdoor dining, lounging, and enjoying the poolside ambiance. A 2 story solarium brings ample natural light and a great source to reduce energy cost. You are practically minutes out to the beltway and enjoying a park-like setting; can't get better than this. One of the best school pyramids (Mantua/Frost/Woodson).

Beautiful single family home with peaceful, private, and spacious back yard.   Come home to a quiet circle drive, private driveway, and one level living with three bedrooms and bathroom on the main level.  Walk in the front door to a living room with a wood burning fireplace, separate dining room, and wrap around deck just outside for easy entertaining.  The basement has a large family room, bathroom, bedroom/office, and storage room...with plenty of options for flexible use.  Walk out of the basement to another outdoor space with a concrete patio, private back yard, and shed.  The perfect balance of a peaceful quite neighborhood but still just a short trip to all the shops and restaurants at the Mosaic District, Falls Church, and Columbia Pike.
column361: Russell Arkin Your Home Sold Guaranteed

column23: Nestled in the desirable Broyhill Crest Community, this charming all brick home is ready for you to make it your own.   This home is situated on a quarter acre lot with beautiful landscaping throughout the yard and large deck on rear of home to enjoy the secluded yard.  Home boasts a large addition (35x14) on the back adding one additional bedroom and den to make this property a 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home.  Additional rooms in finished basement provide living space for you and your family.  One Full bathroom on each level, with tons of potential.  All major components of the home have been replaced and are in excellent condition.  2018 Water Heater, 2016 HVAC, 2014 Architectural Shingle roof.  Main level features hardwood flooring under the carpets.  Come give this home some interior TLC and make it the dream home you have always desired.  Attic is huge for storage and has flooring installed.  Seller has relocated and is selling the property as is - all inspections for informational purposes only.  This commuter’s dream is located inside the beltway with proximity to 495, 395, 50 and numerous Metro stations. Equally appealing is the convenient location to numerous local parks and nature trails. Mason Crest ES, Broyhill Crest Rec Center, and only 8 minutes to Mosaic District's shopping and restaurants!

Location / location / location!  This lovely UPDATED Burke home has 5 bedrooms & 3 full bathrooms.  It is ideally located on a quiet cul-de-sac & sits  on a quarter on an acre with a fully fenced backyard.  This home has close access to one of the largest of the 5 Burke pools & community centers.  The Burke Centre Parkway is also nearby.  Step into this recently updated home & be wowed by the spaciousness! There is plenty of space for "together times" as well a plenty of space for "private times".  This lovely  home has a totally updated white kitchen along with newer stainless steel appliances, granite countertops & a bright adjoining breakfast nook with a  coveted bay window for plants or pillows.  With no carpet on this entire level, it also features a formal dining room & a convenient living room area.  The best part of this level though is the screened-in porch where you can retreat & enjoy the peace of your backyard.  Moving down a few steps gives you easy access to a large family room with a brick wood-burning fireplace!  Bedroom #5 is also located here & because it features a separate outside access from a nearby door plus a full-size updated bathroom, it is ideal as a mother-in-law or au pair suite.  This level also has a large laundry & storage area!  The lowest 4th level is untouched awaiting your specific wishes - more storage needs or perhaps a  large game or media room to enjoy.  Upstairs there are 4 good-sized bedrooms. One is a large primary suite with multiple closets & a beautiful updated primary bathroom.  The hall bathroom has also been recently updated.  Most of the windows in this home have been replaced!   Enjoy being part of the coveted Robinson Secondary School pyramid.  This is also an excellent home with easy commute options via  the Burke VRE, Commuter lots or the Fairfax County Parkway to the Franconia Springfield Metro line.

Welcome Home to Charming!  5966 New England Woods Dr. is located an idyllic street in amenity-filled Burke Centre. With a landscaped lot nestled on a pipe-stem and backing to common grounds, this meticulously maintained 4 BR / 3.5 BA home features beautiful renovations including the kitchen, all baths, lower level with wet bar, and so much more. Find beautiful hardwoods in the foyer, family, dining and living rooms. The kitchen with wood-grain luxury vinyl tile flooring and crisp white cabinets was updated in 2020 with all new stainless steel appliances, backsplash and quartz counters. From the kitchen enter the dining room that flows into the spacious and bright living room with bay window; perfect for entertaining. Head into the cozy family room with fireplace framed in stone and built-in bookshelves and cabinets. Upstairs the spacious primary ensuite bedroom with plenty of closet space, features a renovated bath with skylight, walk-in shower and separate soaking tub. Three additional bright and cheery bedrooms, each with a ceiling fan share a hall bath renovated in 2020. The finished walk-out lower level provides a rec room with new wet bar with beverage fridge,  built-ins and a full bath renovated in 2020 .  A bonus room suits as an office or exercise room. Completing this level find laundry and plenty of storage in the utility room. Other recent updates include but not limited to: hardy wood-grain LVT on the upper (2021) and lower (2020) level floors. Roof and attic fan replaced in 2019. Driveway replaced in 2023. See complete list of updates in the “Documents” section. Located within the Burke Centre Conservancy, an award-winning 1,700 acre Planned Residential Community (PRC), amenities abound including 5 pools, tennis courts, volleyball and basketball courts, community centers, tot lots and miles walking paths. Shopping at major retailers is just minutes away. Discover nearby quaint neighborhood restaurants, go fishing or play golf at Burke Lake, attend classes at GMU or NVCC, visit libraries, see wonderful art at The Workhouse in Lorton, meet friends at Paradise Springs Winery, Bunnyman Brewery, or head to the Historic town of Clifton. Commuters will appreciate the Burke and Rolling Rd. VREs, FFX & Connector bus stops, Fairfax County Parkway, I-495 and I-395 are just minutes away.  Visit the Open House on 9/16 & 9/17 from 1-3pm.

Welcome to your future home in the highly sought-after Sleepy Hollow Run neighborhood! This bright and sunny 5 bedroom, 3 full bath brick home boasts over 3000 finished square feet of living space. Step inside and you'll immediately notice the recently renovated kitchen with its large eat-in area and bay window looking out to the newly fenced back yard. The kitchen is complete with slate appliances, granite countertops, and a beautiful backsplash that adds a warm touch. Refinished hardwood floors throughout the main level add warmth and charm to the home. Downstairs, a large rec room with home theater set up and pool table is the perfect spot for entertaining guests. The wood-burning fireplace adds a cozy touch on chilly evenings. The large sunroom off the dining room offers even more space for entertainment or relaxation. And if you're in the mood for some pampering, the 7-person 56-jet premium acrylic bench spa hot tub will be waiting for you. This home also features a convenient carport and easy access to 395/495. You can even walk to the nearby park! Don't miss your chance to own this wonderful home in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in the area. Schedule a showing today and make this house your own!

Welcome home to 6478 Lake Meadow Drive—a beautiful 5500 SQFT home, located within the highly desirable Edgewater community of Burke! This stately home sits on a .6-acre lot, with the most serene walkway designed by a landscape architect. On the main level you'll find a grand 2-story foyer opening to the office on one side and the formal living room and dining room on the other side. Walk straight back to the showpiece chef’s kitchen featuring Thermador appliances, high-end cabinetry, gas cooking and an entertainer’s island. The sun-filled breakfast room has access to the deck and is open to the 2-story great room, featuring a gas fireplace, skylights and a second staircase to the upper level. The main level is complete with a half bath, laundry room and a 2-car garage. On the upper level you'll find the primary suite with a large walk-in closet, two additional bedrooms, one with private access to the hall bathroom and a 4thbedroom with private full bath in its own wing. In the walk-up lower level, you’ll find an exercise room, full bathroom, ample storage, and a large rec room with two gas fireplaces! The backyard is the perfect space for entertaining on the deck, brick patio, or the flat lush grass. Located minutes from shops, restaurants, parks and feeding into a top-rated school pyramid.

Absolutely GORGEOUS! Well maintained and bright with 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths condo in Lafayette Forest. Granite countertop with SS appliances. Hardwood floors throughout.  Updated both bathrooms and kitchen.  Living room with fireplace leading to patio.  Washer and dryer in unit. Built-in bookshelf in living room.

Welcome to this well-maintained 3 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom townhome in the desirable Burke Centre neighborhood. This townhome offers tremendous value with the  numerous recent updates and upgrades in 2021-2023. This home is move-in ready. Some of the key updates/upgrades include: - Brand-new roof - Energy-efficient LED lighting throughout the home - Fresh basement flooring - A fully renovated kitchen featuring subway backsplash and quartz counters - New dishwasher - Spacious deck for outdoor enjoyment - 2 month old clothes washer and dryer - newly installed sump pump and attic fan - New hardwood floors in the primary bedroom and second bedroom - Kitchenette in the basement - All new toilets  This townhome has just under 2,500 finished square feet and is located across the street from a shopping center (Starbucks, Walmart, Wendys, Giant, Cafe Rio) and minutes walk to Terra Centre, the assigned elementary school. Some additional features of the location include:  - Middle/high school: Robinson - Easy transportation options with a bus stop just outside the house - VRE train station located 2.5 miles away for a stress-free commute - Two assigned parking spots just steps away from the front door  This townhome in Burke offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and modern updates. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your new home. Schedule your viewing today or plan on attending the open houses scheduled for Saturday and Sunday.

Welcome to your dream home nestled in the desirable Red Fox Forest neighborhood, conveniently located just off Braddock Road in Annandale. This stunning originally owned rarely available four level split level property boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, offering ample space for comfortable living. A light-filled open floor plan complete with an amazing chef's kitchen including a breakfast nook that overlooks the beautifully landscaped front yard, cabinetry with tons of storage, all new stainless-steel appliances, and quartz counter tops. The open living room and dining room are perfect for entertaining. Step out from your dining room onto your lovely patio, ideal for outdoor dining.  The home is freshly painted and highlighted with new light fixtures and views of the rear yard oasis. The main level with freshly refinished hardwood floors is the ideal living level. Three spacious bedrooms and two fully updated bathrooms finish out the upper level. But that's not all - the lower-level family room with fireplace (as is) completes this home with a fourth bedroom / home office, updated bath, and rear yard access. A huge partially finished basement level storage room with built-in storage shelving and laundry has so much potential as a home gym, play area, or craft space.  The large fully fenced in rear yard backs to a wooded area and is the perfect retreat for your year-round staycation. This home is not only aesthetically pleasing but also energy-efficient, thanks to a new heat pump and highly efficient (R48) attic insulation. You can relish in the comfort of a well-insulated home while also reducing your environmental footprint - beyond move in ready!  Red Fox Forest is a beautiful and mature community in the highly sought-after Canterbury Woods/Frost/Woodson Pyramid. Annual neighborhood gatherings, a community gazette and the oldest neighborhood watch in Fairfax County make this community so unique. Enjoy and easy commute via bus (17), VRE, I495, I395 and I95. Access to tons of recreational facilities, including local trails, the Audrey Moore Rec Center with pool, Eagle Bank Arena and the Kings Park Library. This will be more than just a house - it will become your HOME!

Prime location! Welcome home to this charming 4 bedroom/2.2 bath colonial in the heart of Burke Centre. This lovely home offers commuting convenience and has been beautifully maintained. You'll fall in love with the easy floor plan offering tons of space! Hardwood-style flooring on all 3 levels. Main level features an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops with an adjoining breakfast area leading to the deck and backyard. Also on this level is a large family room and separate living/dining room perfect for entertaining. Upper level offers 4 generous sized bedrooms, 2 renovated full baths and a laundry chute for your convenience. The lower level rec room is perfect for game/movie night. All this can be found in the Burke Centre community offering fabulous amenities including access to outdoor pools, tennis courts, community centers, common grounds, nature paths, picnic areas, playgrounds, and so much more! **** Commuters will appreciate the close proximity to the Fairfax County Parkway, Route 123, I-495, Express Lanes, Metro Bus and the VRE (with garage parking), and other major driving routes. Close proximity to George Mason University campus, major shopping centers within Burke Centre and a Farmer's Market on Saturdays at the VRE station are other pluses to this location. **** Outdoor enthusiasts will love the local parks including Burke Lake Park with 888 acres of natural beauty surrounding a sparkling 218-acre lake, and everyone will enjoy the diverse shopping, dining, and entertainment choices available throughout the area. If you are looking for a fabulous home filled with natural light and quality upgrades in a fantastic community, this is it. A wonderful turnkey property! Welcome home.

Showings Begin on Saturday AM.   Tremendous value - INSIDE the beltway!   Very well-maintained 3 bedroom, 2 full bath Rambler with addition on a gorgeous, 1/2 acre lot with stately trees, colorful flower beds and mature plantings.  Located near convenient commuting routes 395, 495, Route 50 as well as the VRE METRO Blue Line. Enjoy quiet living in a “tucked in” neighborhood of oversized lots near shopping, entertainment, county parks (Deerlick, Green Spring Gardens), the popular Pinecrest public 9-hole golf course and the sought-after Jefferson High School for Science and Technology.    This house has been thoughtfully expanded to include a combination Family Room / Kitchen living space with gas fireplace that provides a wonderful centralized activity space, for social gatherings, family food events or TV watching.  The kitchen has stainless steel appliances (new), stainless steel double sink, lustrous oak hard wood cabinets and spacious Corian counters and Corian island / breakfast bar.   Also part of the expansion is an adjoining 21’ x 18’ covered screened porch and attached 18’  x 18’ Trex-built deck.  Both outdoor spaces provide wonderful social and entertaining space as well as breathtaking panoramic views of the expansive backyard.    The lower level provides lots of recreation space, an additional room with closet that has been used as a bedroom but does not meet all of the county codes to be considered a legal bedroom.  Also on the lower level is a large utility room / laundry room as well as expanded 3 car garage / workshop.    The house boasts beautiful oak hardwood floors throughout the main level of the original house, replacement insulated  windows, new lighting and partial bathroom updates.  The house has been completely repainted and is in move-in condition. Recent systems upgrades include new architectural shingle roof with ridge venting / gutters guards,  a generous layer of blown insulation and a newer 90% efficient HVAC system.

This lovingly updated Brighton model, 4 bedroom, 3-½ bath townhome by Berry builders is surprisingly spacious inside! You’ll enjoy having over 2,500 square feet of living space to spread out in, plus great outdoor living areas on the deck, rear covered porch, and privacy-fenced patio to enjoy for relaxing and entertaining.   The main level of this home has hardwood floors throughout, welcoming living room and dining room areas, plus the updated eat-in gourmet kitchen and a bright sunny family room with vaulted ceiling and skylights and a cozy gas-burning fireplace.  The primary bedroom suite has vaulted ceilings, deep dormer-style windows with plantation shutters, two large closets (one walk-in), and a gorgeous fully renovated primary bath.  You’ll love having three bedrooms and two full baths upstairs, plus a fourth bedroom and another full bath on the lower level.  The lower level also has a large rec room that walks out to the covered porch and patio, plus added storage beneath the stairs and a utility room.   Burke Centre residents enjoy abundant community amenities such as walking/jogging trails, community centers with tennis and pickleball courts, five community pools (membership required), tot lots, basketball and volleyball and other sports facilities, plus ponds and a lake and more. Best of all, one of these community centers (The Ponds) is just around the corner from this home!  Within a mile or two, you’ll find numerous options for shopping and dining, schools and places of worship, bus stops and the Burke VRE station, and so much more. This neighborhood is served by Fairfax County Public Schools’ excellent Terra Centre Elementary and Robinson Secondary schools.

LUXURY!   ELEGANCE!  **3-car garage single house with 6,300 square feet of luxurious living space in Annandale.** The home was custom built with impeccable taste and meticulous attention to detail throughout the house. Artist-designed Italian draperies help create warmth and charm for the home. All gorgeous draperies do come with your new home.  Hardwood floors on main level, Main level with elegant living room, a formal dining room, library, gourmet kitchen with a center-island, bright sun-room leading to the deck.  Beautiful 20ft tall Stone fireplace!!!   Upper level 4 bedrooms 3 full bath including a luxury master bedroom suite with a comfy sitting room with a vaulted ceiling, with soaking tub, double vanity and features three closets. Finished basement with recreation room and Full baths, Bed room or offices that can be used as guest rooms Flat backyard   No HOA!!!  Appointment only to show. Call agent for details.

Well-maintained by the original owners, this sunny single-family home sits in a trees/cul de sack to the back and the circular space in the neighborhood in front of the house provides plenty of serenity and peace.  Very large 5 spacious bedroom 4.5 bath estate home with approximately 5,819 SQFT over 3 fully finished levels with attached 2 car garage and rubber made resin shed.  As you enter this home, you are greeted foyer with a chandelier that opens to the living room with a bay window and a family room with French doors.  French doors provide the convenience of using the family room and living room as open and closed flexible spaces. The private family room with built-in bookcases, a fireplace, and an upgraded coffered ceiling.   To the right of the foyer is the spacious dining room with a cozy porched balcony  Well-stocked granite counter tops, custom-modified gourmet, modern kitchen surrounded by a large island with stainless steel appliances, and two wall ovens kitchen with access to a huge Trex deck, and a beautiful backyard with tree views.  The cozy library is next to the garage and half bath.  The modern touch of expanded wainscoting and moldings throughout the main level. Upstairs via a private staircase are 4 spacious en-suite bedrooms with ceiling fans. The Master bedroom suite with a large sitting area, two closets,  an ensuite bathroom with double vanities, and a jacuzzi tub. There are three additional spacious bedrooms upstairs with 2 bedrooms sharing a jack-and-jill full bathroom and 1 bedroom with a private bathroom.  Hardwood floors in all houses except the basement floor, all custom curtains convey   Fully finished sunfilled, walk-out basement (additional 1,819sq ft. of living space), large open custom entertainment area with wet bar, kitchenette, one additional bedroom, and full bath, and extra finished storage space that can be used in a gym or good for storing quantities.  Outside property features: unique brick front/side and, porch entrance (covered front entry and dining room balcony),  curb appeal hardscaping, and a home backs to open space with private trees-  open view of the rear yard. stone/pebbled patio,  Trex deck, Roof -30 year architecture single  Home improvements: NEW HVAC 2022, All New LED light bulbs, New customs modern paint cabinets, New paint/main, upper  level, NEW paint /porch at the front   Excellent location, easy access to RT 495(3 miles), Rt95, Rt395,    16 Miles to Amazon headquarters!   Great commuter location close to all major routes and prime locations, Lake Braddock middle/high school zone;  access to bus and bicycle commute, delicious restaurants nearby, park, recreation centers, VRE station,  and shopping are minutes away at Tyson’s Corner & Mosaic.  It’s centrally located between two major airports, DCA & Dulles.

**TO BE BUILT-DELIVERY FOR SPRING  2024 VISIT OUR MODEL 4053 THORNTON STREET ANNANDALE VA. Presenting 'The Wedgewood' executive series custom home to be built by Premier Homes Group LLC. This pre-sale opportunity offers the ability to select your own finishes and make a truly custom home. The gorgeous transitional potential 6 bedroom, 6 full and 2 half bath home is offering all the luxuries home buyers seek and located in a fabulous location nestled on a .45 acre lot. Open floor plan, potential hardwood floors on main level and primary suite, high ceilings, an abundance of windows, decorative moldings, on trend 3 tone paint, formal living room, dining room, stunning chef's kitchen with high-end stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, large center island and morning room opening to a spacious family room with cozy gas fireplace. Mudroom with built-in bench. Powder room on main level plus convenient bedroom and private ensuite bath on main level. Upstairs, the luxurious primary suite boasts a sitting room, dual walk in closets, and ensuite bath with freestanding soaking tub and expansive walk in shower with dual shower heads, built-in seat and frameless glass. 3 additional bedrooms each with walk in closets and ensuite baths. Bedroom level laundry room with quartz countertops. Minutes from the beltway, 395, Fairfax Hospital, Pentagon, Mosaic and DC.  PHOTOS are of similar model

Open House Sunday, 2-4!***Beautiful end unit in a picturesque setting in sought after Town of Herndon! Gorgeous landscaping in the front and back! Extra-large fenced backyard and the home is surrounded by acres and acres of HOA maintained green space! This 3 bed, 2.5 bath townhouse is move-in ready! You'll love the kitchen and all the wonderful updates like pull out drawers, super large sink, new faucet and plenty of counter space! Updated HVAC! Fresh paint throughout! The upper level features a bright primary suite with attached private bath! In addition there are spacious bedrooms and a beautifully updated hall bathroom! Four Seasons has wonderful amenities including tot lots, outdoor pool, tennis courts, TONS of green space, and ABUNDANT parking- such a rare thing in a townhome community. Minutes to Dulles airport, and in between TWO metro stations! Run, don't walk!

**NEW CONSTRUCTION, TO BE BUILT**  PHOTOS ARE OF SIMILAR HOME**This home has it all...Excellent location, superb quality and the latest architectural design.  Fantastic Open Floor Plan with high ceilings, oversize rooms and luxurious finishes.  This home offers up to  6 bedrooms, all with ensuite bathrooms, and as many as 2 powder rooms.  There can be a  finished third floor with living area, bedroom and full bath.  The potentially finished lower level has a separate entrance, bedroom with ensuite bathroom, living area and full wet bar.  Excellent location close to the  Beltway, Tysons Corner, Fairfax Hospital, Washington DC, and the Mosaic District.  For more information visit our model home Thursday through Sunday 10 AM to 6 PM.  4053 Thornton Street Annandale, Va.  22003.

Well loved home in the heart of Herndon! Gleaming hardwood floors throughout. Entry into bright 2 story foyer. Updated windows bring in loads of natural light. Spacious family room with wood burning fireplace. Formal living room and dining room with sliding glass doors which lead to private fenced backyard with patio and shed. Upper level boasts spacious secondary bedrooms, full hall bath and primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings and primary bathroom. Full finished basement with recreation room, den, full bathroom and laundry/utility room. Newer roof and HVAC systems. The home is close to schools, major commuter roads and minutes to Downtown Herndon (shops, restaurants, festivals), Silver Line Metro and Dulles International Airport.

**TO BE BUILT-DELIVERY FOR SPRING 2024***PLEASE VISIT ONE OF OUR MODEL HOMES 4053 THORNTON ST. ANNANDALE, VA.  22003 AND 6506 HALLS FARM LANE MCLEAN, VA. 22101.  OPEN THURS-MON 10-6*** Presenting 'The Idylwood' executive series custom home to be built by Premier Homes Group LLC. This pre-sale opportunity offers the ability to select your own finishes and make a truly custom home. The Gorgeous transitional 6 bedroom, 7 full and 2 half bath home is offering all the luxuries home buyers seek and located in a fabulous location nestled on a .55 acre lot. Open floor plan, hardwood floors on main level and primary suite, high ceilings, an abundance of windows, decorative moldings, on trend 3 tone paint, formal living room, dining room, stunning chef's kitchen with high-end stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, large center island and morning room opening to a spacious family room with cozy gas fireplace. Mudroom with built-in bench. Powder room on main level plus convenient bedroom and private ensuite bath on main level. Upstairs, the luxurious primary suite boasts a sitting room, dual walk in closets, and ensuite bath with freestanding soaking tub and expansive walk in shower with dual shower heads, built-in seat and frameless glass. 3 additional junior suites each with walk in closets and ensuite baths. Bedroom level laundry room with quartz countertops.  Guest suite with loft area.  Still time to customize/make buyer selections. All this in an excellent location near 495, Fairfax Hospital, The Mosaic District, Tysons Corner and Washington DC .

Excellent condo in the center of Herndon. Metro just a mile away. Nearby Dulles Airport for those that need access for commuting. Lovely community with outdoor pool. Unit has one dedicated parking space and plenty of guest parking. Unit has plenty of space and excellent balcony view from the top floor.

This spacious 4 bedroom, 4.5 bath home is set on a large ½ acre private corner lot and is located just minutes from I-495, Route 50, Mosaic District, Merrifield and Tysons Corner! With 2 separate garages, this is the ideal property for a car enthusiast or hobbyist to call home! The front entry one-car garage is perfect for the family car with direct access to the kitchen. The second, side-entry 3-bay garage has heat and AC and plenty of room for all your tools and electricity to run them. Whether you’re wrenching on cars, in need of a studio or looking for space to build and refinish furniture, this home is it! Inside this lovely home you will find hardwood floors throughout; a wood-burning fireplace with custom-built surround and mantle; vaulted ceilings; custom hand-crafted bookshelves, desk and file drawers off the spacious living room and dining room; a dream laundry/mudroom with custom hand-crafted cabinetry, granite countertops, and a full bath; and a stunning newly renovated custom kitchen with cabinetry handmade by the current owner. Here, no detail was overlooked from the floor-to-ceiling cabinets with a rolling ladder to reach high shelves, center-island Viking 6-burner gas range, second electric oven and built-in Viking microwave, to the stone and butcherblock countertops, second prep sink, and beverage center with 2 refrigerators. There’s even a hidden room above the kitchen that can only be accessed through a cabinet door! Two primary suites offer multi-generational options. One is located on the main level, and the other spans the entire second floor creating a spacious and private retreat! The upstairs primary suite includes a large sunken tub and separate glass shower enclosure with rain-head showerhead, two separate vanities, and lots of closet space including two walk-in closets.  Two additional bedrooms on the main level are adjacent to the fourth full bath, and the main level also includes a separate family room adjacent to a spacious sunroom that overlooks the large backyard and deck and provides access to the 3-car garage. Brand new hot water heater in 2023, the exterior has been freshly painted and the front driveway was just resurfaced, too many other updates to list. Welcome home!

Elegant Colonial in Shaker Woods! This meticulously maintained 4 bedroom plus den, 2 full/2 half bath home is sited on a quiet cul-de-sac and features loads of natural light, large windows, a 2-story foyer, and designer touches throughout. The fully updated, eat-in kitchen boasts wood floors, granite counters, a center island, and a spacious breakfast area with bay window! The kitchen opens to a family room boasting a vaulted ceiling with skylights, a fireplace, and French doors leading to the 2-tiered deck and private wooded backyard! A large dining room with a bay window, a formal living room, a den/ office, a half bath, a laundry room, and an attached 2-car garage complete the main level. The upper level offers 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. The expansive en-suite primary bedroom features a roomy sitting area, a cozy window seat, a walk-in closet, and a spacious bath with dual vanity and jacuzzi tub. The lower level includes an oversized recreation room with sliding doors to the backyard, a bonus room, a half bath, and storage galore! The almost half-acre lot boasts gorgeous landscaping, mature trees, and flowering plants and shrubs.  Conveniently located near commuter routes — Fairfax County Parkway, Routes 66, 7, and 267 (Dulles Toll Road) — and the Reston Metro! Shaker Woods is just short trip to Reston Town Center, Tysons Corner, Dulles Airport, and all that Northern Virginia has to offer!

ONE of a KIND! Spacious, Completely Renovated 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths and NO HOA! The home is Freshly painted Inside and Out! Brand New Carpet, Brand New Flooring Throughout. Brand New Windows! The kitchen provides ample counter space, Custom 42" Soft Close Cabinets and wine rack, Brand New SS appliances & a gourmet Double Oven with an Air-Fryer Stove and an oversized kitchen sink.  Spacious living room and half bath on the main level for convenience. The primary bedroom provides the perfect environment to rest and recharge featuring an ensuite bathroom with double vanity sinks and a versatile shower with 2-shower heads! The Walk-Out basement offers a Kitchenette with a full bath and flex Room. Relax with multiple outdoor living spaces including a covered front porch and rear deck. This home features a 2 car garage. Walk to Downtown Herndon, Minutes away from Reston Town Center. Conveniently located to Dulles International Airport. Close to Route 7 and Dulles Toll Road.

This beautiful home is ready for its new owners. Light filled with hardwood floors on main and upper levels were just refinished. Fresh paint from top to bottom. New roof, new stove, built-in bookcases. The basement is a walkout with tons of natural light. A large backyard for entertaining. Excellent commuter location just off 495 in the heart of Annandale. Must see!!

Fantastic and newly updated end unit townhome in the heart of Herndon. You will be amazed at all the sunlight coming from three sides through large window, and you won't believe how big this place feels. A fourth bedroom has been added which makes this home very unique in the neighborhood and surrounding area. Updates too many to mention but they've brought this home into the 21st century, and opened up the space for today's buyers, and the new layout stands out in the neighborhood. Privacy fenced rear yard with patio area and extra storage. Great value for the money based on recent comps and surrounding neighborhoods. Vacant and ready for you to move in and make it your own!

Welcome to 3542 Coker Place, a tastefully renovated and impeccably maintained colonial nestled within the tranquility of a secluded Annandale cul-de-sac. This remarkable four-bedroom, three-and-a-half-bathroom gem boasts an expansive interior with versatile spaces and private outdoor retreats perfectly suited for all your entertainment aspirations.  Upon crossing the threshold, an inviting foyer unfolds, flanked by an elegant formal dining room to the right and a gracious first living room to the left. A convenient half bathroom discreetly adjoins this area. Continuing your journey, the home opens into a modernized kitchen adorned with luxurious granite countertops, complemented by a second inviting living room and a comfortable family room. With a seamless transition, the French doors from the kitchen open to a generously proportioned, freshly updated deck crafted from composite wood. This outdoor haven gracefully descends to a meticulously designed hardscaped patio. Beyond, a charming walkway leads to an additional secluded patio space, ideal for creating moments of reprieve.  Ascending to the upper level, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, each thoughtfully appointed and graced with ample closet space. Two full bathrooms feature heated floors and dual vanities in the primary bathroom.   The basement unveils a fully self-contained living area, perfect for accommodating long-term guests or exploring short-term rental possibilities. This versatile space includes a well-equipped kitchen, a contemporary full bathroom, a tranquil bedroom, an inviting recreation room, and an enclosed walk-up area with its own private entrance.   It doesn’t stop there. This property includes a spacious driveway, as well as a two-car garage thoughtfully designed to accommodate your storage needs. The home also showcases various updates, including a new dishwasher and microwave with exterior venting, recessed lighting throughout, a newer HVAC system (installed in 2016), and protective gutter guards.  Ideally located, this residence offers effortless access to major thoroughfares such as I-495, Little River Turnpike, Annandale Road, and Gallows Road. In addition, it enjoys proximity to esteemed institutions like INOVA Fairfax and the vibrant Mosaic District. This is more than just a home; it's a testament to a lifestyle where sophistication, convenience, and comfort harmoniously converge.

Downtown Herndon Location in Sought After Lifestyle Condos-Wood Laminate Floors Throughout- Huge Living Room with Sliding Glass Door to Balcony-Overlooks Gorgeous Common Area-Separate Dining Room off Kitchen-Stacked Washer & Dryer-Community Pool

Large spacious owner's suite with walk in closet and updated bath plus seasonal closet. A lower-level den with closet plus finished storage room along with the just redone lower bath makes a perfect retreat for guests. This home has been well maintained and is in good condition but is being sold 'as is' inspections for informational purposes only.

column23: Welcome to Hiddenbrook, in the heart of Herndon! This 3-bed, 2-bath rambler offers a warm, open-concept living area, well-lit and perfect for gatherings. The kitchen is spacious with modern amenities. The primary bedroom has an en-suite bath for privacy, and two extra bedrooms provide flexibility. A standout feature is the ample backyard space and patio, ideal for entertaining or relaxing after a long day.. Sold "as is," this property offers plenty of room to make it your own. Commuter's delight with easy access to Dulles Airport, Route 7, Fairfax County Parkway, Route 28, and the Toll Road. Close to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Don't miss this opportunity for suburban tranquility with urban convenience. Schedule a showing today!

**Photos are of similar model**Please visit the furnished model home at 4053 Thornton St, Open Daily**Premier Homes Group proudly presents their Executive Series Wedgewood model at Red Oak Manor sitting on a .36 acre premium lot backing to open space in a new development adjacent to five other similar homes. The open floor plan with 10’ ceilings throughout the main level is complemented with high-end finishes from7.5” European White Oak hardwood floors, decorative moldings, upgraded lighting, and windows to the floor creating a light and airy atmosphere throughout.  The gorgeous grand kitchen is a chef's delight with an abundance of pristine white traditional and glass front cabinetry, GE Café Series stainless steel appliances, including a 48” 6-burner dual fuel oven gas range, pot filler, range hood, built-in microwave/wall oven and 48” built in fridge and an impressive, oversized island with a stunning waterfall quartz countertop. The main level also features a private study and an additional main level bedroom suite. The upper-level features 10’ ceilings and 4 bedrooms, each with its own private en-suite bath. The luxurious owner's suite boasts a sitting room with gas fireplace, a screened porch, dual walk-in closets, and ensuite bath with freestanding soaking tub, dual water closets and expansive frameless glass ultra walk-in shower with built-in seat. All secondary bedrooms and laundry room have shaker door cabinetry and quartz countertops. The fully finished lower-level features 10’ ceilings and includes a bedroom with a full bath, family lounge with fireplace and wet bar, exercise room and luxurious spa retreat with a sauna and steam shower.  Premier Homes Group takes pride in using nothing but the best of quality building materials. From the structural components to the smallest details. All this in an excellent location and friendly community with easy access to 495 and I-66. Everyone will love the diverse shopping, dining, parks and entertainment choices in every direction.

Bright & cozy  townhome 3 Bedroom with 2.5 Bathroom.  Vacant, ready to move in, Fresh paint,  , Fully Renovated  recently three years , updated  kitchen counter top & cabinet and stainless steel appliances.   Vinyl floor though whole house. remodel two full bath,   windows & HVAC. water heater .Large family room walk to patio  with fully fenced /storage shed  , back to community area & trees. 2 parking spaces, 1 assigned + 1 free and street parking available. Located in Reflection Lake,  access to the private pool, tennis & basketball courts, and playgrounds. Right off the Dulles Toll Rd. close school & multi shopping center, bus, metro station.

Magnificent renovated cul-de-sac home in a secluded and quiet community featuring gourmet eat-in kitchen with granite countertops, large center island & dinette; sunlight-filled family room with Palladian windows, expensive crystal chandelier & gas fireplace; hardwood floors; high ceilings; dual staircases to upper level; walkout basement with full kitchen; 3 master suites; large 2 decks off main and lower levels; 2 car garage with 4 cars driveway parking; private backyard with mature trees. Commuters dream location with easy access to major routes (I-495, Gallows Rd, Annadale Rd).

Rare opportunity to own a WATERFRONT END UNIT on Lake Braddock. Open floor plan on the main level, kitchen open to dining room overlooking the living room with vaulted ceilings and living room walks out to low maintenance deck overlooking the lake and side deck and stairs to walk down to the lower level.  Gorgeous 4-Bedroom /3.5 Bath house in Prime Burke Location!  Fantastic POND View from All levels that is the most wonderful advantage of this house, and it protects your privacy so that you can enjoy nature in the middle of the city. Each floor has it's own balcony that allows your independent space.  This house has been renovated newer Kitchen w/42" Maple cab, Stainless Appliances, Hardwood floors on 2 levels, and  laminated floor in the walk out basement level. (NO CARPET in this house).  Newer windows and updated baths. Lower level has a full bathroom  walks out to the patio and spacious, fenced backyard overlooking the lake.  Community amenities include 2 swimming pools, tennis courts, basketball, playgrounds & community center. Kayak or fish right from your home! Walks around the lake along a lovely walking path just beyond the backyard. Recent updates - New roof in 2020, refinished hardwood floors, new carpet on the lower level, New fence in 2023. Private, tucked away location on the end. 2 reserved parking spots just out front. 2-minute walk to bus 17K direct to the Pentagon. 6 minutes to the VRE and the Pohick Stream Valley/VRE Trail Best of all worlds having a lakefront home with shopping, restaurants, brewery and transit just minutes away!

Only structural selections have been appointed and all interior colors/styles may still be selected for a limited time! Photos are of a previously built Cameron floorplan.

Bright and airy second floor unit with covered balcony in a secure building with elevators. Additional visitor parking is directly around the corner in front of the clubhouse, and throughout the community.  ***  Brand new flooring, paint and more (September 2023).  ***  Ideally located 1/2 mile from Worldgate Centre,  1 mile from multiple grocery stores, 2 miles from the heart of Historic Downtown Herndon,  2 miles from Herndon Silver Line Metro rail station and a 0.4 mile walk to the Chandon Dog Park.  ***  Community amenities are plentiful and include a clubhouse, party room, gym, pool, common areas, and more.

OPEN Floor plan*** LARGE Living Room w/ recessed light and Huge Wall to wall window*** Kitchen features Stainless steel appliances, gas oven/range, GRANITE countertops open to Dining Area*** Plenty of cabinet space and island*** Enjoy the outdoors on the concrete over-sized balcony*** LARGE Bedrooms w/ mirror closets*** Common washer & dryer in same level*** Building has an elevator and intercom system*** Close to shops, restaurants*** Easy access to 495 and walking distance to bus stops***MOVE IN READY!!!

Welcome to 202 Meeting House Station Sq, where your dream home awaits. This meticulously maintained four-level townhouse, perfectly situated in the heart of Herndon, effortlessly blends modern convenience with timeless charm, creating an ideal sanctuary.  Spacious Elegance: This townhome boasts a generously proportioned and open floor plan, perfectly tailored for both everyday living and entertaining. The main level showcases a gourmet kitchen with sleek stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a central island, crisp white cabinets, and an updated backsplash. It seamlessly connects to the family room with a cozy fireplace. The separate living and dining area combination extends to a balcony, providing an ideal outdoor retreat.  Owner's Retreat: The third level is dedicated to the primary bedroom, a generously sized suite complete with a walk-in closet featuring built-in shelving and a spa-like en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and a shared full bathroom offer comfortable accommodations for friends and guests.  Outdoor Bliss: Step onto your private deck to savor your morning coffee or bask in the outdoors; it's the perfect spot to relax and rejuvenate.  Garage with Electric Car Charger: Notably, this home features a two-car garage equipped with an electric car charger, ensuring both convenience and sustainability.  Prime Location: Positioned just moments away from Herndon's vibrant downtown, this townhouse offers the ultimate convenience, with an array of dining, shopping, and entertainment options at your doorstep. Commuters will appreciate the ease of access to major roadways, including the Dulles Toll Road and Route 28.  Don't let this incredible opportunity slip away. Schedule a showing today to experience all that this home has to offer, and make it your new home in Herndon's vibrant community.

Insanely gorgeous home in beautiful Lake Braddock.  We can't get enough of this stunning house, nor could the photgrapher! Come and enjoy the beautiful artwork in the home, painted by an acclaimed local artist, a woman who raised her large family in this home.  The family decided to honor their wonderful mother and restore this home by taking it down to the studs and putting it back together with the most incredible attention to detail. Redesigned by an interior designer, and with work performed by a caring and wonderful contractor, this home is extremely special. This might be the furthest thing from a flip you can imagine. Ask for a list of all the upgrades included in this home, but features include: fully renovated kitchen and 3.5 bathrooms, new subfloors, drywall, flooring throughout, all new lighting, new Pella windows, brand new deck, huge primary bedroom ensuite with a coffee station, custom shelving, spacious primary bathroom including a soaking tub, separate shower, dual vanity, marble and polished nickel finishes. Every inch of this home has been thoughtfully designed and renovated. There is nothing here left to do other than make it your own.

Welcome home!  Gorgeous brick front, just outside the beltway nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac with luxury renovations and 2-car garage.  This spacious home offers an open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms and a large, finished walk-out lower level.  The lot backs up to a wooded area, which lends to privacy galore and the entire home is bathed in natural light.  Enter the sun-bathed two-story foyer which opens to refinished oak hardwood floors and 9-foot ceilings.  The main floor features a beautifully renovated gourmet kitchen with quartz counter tops, gas range, multi-ovens, pantry and peninsula for ample counter space.  The wine bar with fridge makes it perfect for entertaining guests.  French doors open to the private upper-level deck overlooking nature. Cook out, entertain or relax on the expansive two-level deck.  The great room has a 20-foot vaulted ceiling and a 14-foot stone fireplace - the perfect gathering place. The spacious main floor also offers a large dining room, formal living room and office, which features French doors and custom cabinetry, the ideal space for working from home or quiet study.  Upper level has 3 bedrooms, each with its own en suite with quartz counter tops and bathtubs.  The primary bedroom has a vaulted ceiling and enormous 20-foot walk-in closet.  The spa-like bath is where you can indulge in relaxation with a whirlpool tub, frameless glass shower and private treed views.  Huge, lower-level walk-out rec room offers many options!  It has wide open space, a custom bar, large bedroom and full bath, a workout room, huge storage room and additional closet space.  French doors open to the lower deck, which runs the length of the house and is protected from rain.  Relax on the secluded porch swing and enjoy a good book surrounded by nature and mature trees.  The Mosaic District, Inova Hospital and 495 are just minutes away and the Accotink trail is right around the corner.  Dining, shopping, entertainment, recreation and transportation - you truly have everything at your fingertips.  And most importantly - in the Woodson School Pyramid and no HOA!

Step into this exquisite contemporary 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathroom home that boasts an impressive 4,400+ sq ft of meticulously designed living space, accentuated by soaring 9-foot vaulted ceilings and hard wood floor throughout. On the main level, you'll find a luxurious main bedroom suite with a large en-suite bathroom and an expansive walk-in closet. The gourmet kitchen with all  brand-new top-of-the-line appliances, an abundance of cabinet space, plus a built in pantry, and an  island with showcasing granite slab countertops. From the kitchen, the open-concept layout, flowing effortlessly into the welcoming family room and formal dining area. Imagine creating cherished memories during your festive celebrations as family and friends gather around the spacious island, with the heightening the sense of togetherness and festivity.   As you ascend to the upper level, you'll discover three expansive bedrooms that provide ample space and a full bathroom. Additionally there is an extra 1525 sq ft of finished basement. This versatile space presents an exciting opportunity to function as an independent accessory dwelling unit (ADU), offering potential for rental income or an in-law suite, complete with its own full kitchen, bathroom, and a separate rear entrance. The outside space is truly a delight, nestled on half an acre. The front porch adds a touch of personality to the property, and a splendid stone patio creates an idyllic backdrop for sophisticated summer gatherings. Don't miss out the 2 car garage and extra storage along with a driveway for multiple cars.  Ideally located in close proximity to Dulles Airport,  Downtown Herndon, the Herndon Centennial Public Golf Course is just around the corner.  Reston town center and the Northern Virginia Tech corridor are all a stones throw. Come and see all this property has to offer.

🏡Nestled in the desirable Columbia Pines Community, this lovely 3-bedroom 1.5-bathroom brick home is freshly painted. Beautiful refinished hardwoods on the main level.  Many updates throughout including replacement windows, updated bathrooms (1/2 bath is plumbed for shower/tub) and kitchen. Discover the true potential of space in this home's expansive, newly remodeled lower level with exterior access.  . The thoughtful layout includes a convenient half bath already plumbed for a future bath or shower, while the adjacent laundry room adds an extra layer of functionality to this well-designed space. Move in ready but lots of potential as well. 🌺 The expansive yard is perfect for play and relaxation. It comes alive in spring with hostas, azaleas, rhododendron and more. A little bit of suburbia just inside the beltway! Under a mile to Beanetics coffee shop (a neighborhood favorite), grocery and restaurants. 🎾The community has several parks, biking and walking trails, a recreation center with outdoor pool (with membership) and tennis and basketball courts open for all. 🚗Near I495, Rt 50, I-66, bus stop. Less than 4 miles to Fairfax Hospital and a little over 5 miles to the Mosaic District and Dunn Loring Metro. 💖You're going to love living here!

Welcome to unite 81 at 12245 Wye Oak Commons Cir.  This beautiful townhoume in WALDEN AT BURKE CENTRE is a part of the Burke Centre Conservancy. You get access to the 5 Community Centers, each of which has a swimming pool! Also take advantage of the many other amenities to include tennis courts, pickleball and basketball courts TBP.  There are multiple trails, tot lots and fun events like the Burke Centre Festival! It's conveniently located  near multiple shopping centers, restaurants, and major commuter roads.  A commuters dream with easy access to the VRE Burke Centre Station, Fairfax County Parkway, Burke Centre Parkway, I-495 and more.  Fully finished lower level back to private treed area.  The interior boasts hardwood flooring. Maintenance free unit the association fees include lawn maintenance.

Location, location, location! Minutes from the new Herndon Metro station, this home is in the perfect spot for any Northern Virginia Commuter. It offers many stunning features such as an updated kitchen with granite countertops, main level Studio office perfect for working from home, and office safe, wood burning fireplace in family room, and large corner lot with fully fence backyard for pet security. Enjoy time with family in the spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and tons of natural light.  Pool and tot lots in close proximity to the property. Don't miss this great opportunity!  Current Low interest rate mortgage is assumable pending buyer's approval by lender. Property is leased until April 30th, 2024.

Close to shopping, dinning, VRE and Burke Conservancy pools, tennis, walking trails

This wonderful 3 level townhome offers modern living at its best. The owners have taken great care of their home. This home offers an abundance of light from all the windows throughout. The open floor plan concept on the main level gives you lots of living space.   Updates including repainted cabinets, air conditioning unit, kitchen basin faucet, and bathroom sink basin, and added a new refrigerator, and two ceiling fans.  water heater 2 years old, HVAC replaced 2016, replaced the polybutylene water lines in 2018.   The fully fenced backyard overlooks trees and is conveniently located just of the dining area. 2 reserved parking right out front!  Virginia Ave is not a through street, so no traffic going by the house.  Conveniently located with easy access to Dulles Airport and Rt 7.  Lots of dining, shopping, and entertainment options.

***Price Improvement*** Welcome to 9012 Fort Craig Drive, an impressive contemporary home in excellent condition and move-in ready. Large rooms combined with lots of space are on display in a home that can't miss in Burke Virginia's Carr built Signal Hill neighborhood. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths, including an additional convenient powder room, this Longwood model home offers ample space for comfortable living. The timeless design elements showcase the character of the era, while modern updates ensure convenience. Enjoy the sunlit living spaces and a well-appointed kitchen that beckons for culinary creativity. The lush backyard provides a serene escape, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood, this home combines classic elegance with contemporary amenities, making it an ideal haven for a growing family or anyone seeking a blend of style and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of mid-century charm with all the comforts of today.

Move in ready home you've been waiting for Beautiful. Sunny, Well  maintained 4 bedroom , 4.5  full bath  2 car garage townhome End Unit in the sought  Aspen Hill Ct. in Annandale. "Irving Elevation" model with a handsome Colonial brick facade and large windows, delivers over 3,080 finished square feet(square footage is estimated)  including the finished basement across 4 (Loft) levels . Gorgeous moldings. Palladium window treatments and ample source of natural lights.   Master Bedroom has multiple closets and features a soak tub with dual sinks. There's a full bathroom located in the basement and bathroom on every floor.  The wood floors continue to the first upper level, which features the primary suite with a large en suite bath (featuring double sinks, a large soaking tub and separate shower) and a custom walk-in closet.  Adjacent to the kitchen is the cozy family space with gas fireplace, and sliding doors to the deck - perfect for outside dining and relaxing. Rounding out the main level is the spacious formal living/dining room, gleaming wood floors.  Outdoor deck is an amazing space for showing off your grilling skills while you host guests. Quiet and great location .This home is located close to major commuter routes   (conveniently located near both 395 and 495) offering quick access to DC, the Pentagon, Amazon HQ, Tysons Corner, and any number of other employment centers.  There's even the option to leave the car in the garage and hop a bus at the corner with direct routes to the Pentagon, National Landing,  Amazon HQ.  parks and recreational venues, and shopping and dining options, offering everything for convenient, low-maintenance living. BACK ON THE MARKET!!!  Beautiful Old Dranesville Hunt Club Opportunity! 3,414 finished square feet of welcoming, pretty, and light-filled space! MAIN LEVEL:  custom kitchen (with a one-of-a-kind counter-height walnut kitchen table), separate front facing living and dining rooms, office (with French doors and backyard view), family room (with wooded views of yard, fireplace, peaked ceiling and skylight), and a powder room. UPPER LEVEL: 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, master suite includes hardwood floors, 2 walk in closets, sitting area. BASEMENT LEVEL:  Room for pingpong or pool table, and TV/gaming/lounging area, and a full bath, and a bonus room (currently used as a home gym.) BACKYARD OASIS: Screened gazebo, pond, stone patio, deck, basketball hoop area with bricked in free-throw line). This happy home has proven it can comfortably and graciously accommodate a crowd - whether for a backyard barbecue, watching the big game, or hosting a formal dinner or happy hour. Most of the house was renovated in 2010 including siding, roof, and windows. The active neighborhood hosts events year round (4th of July Parade, Chili Cook-offs, Holiday Events, and more!) Walk to miles of wooded creek trails (entrance at end of street), Old Town Herndon (1 mile), W&OD bike trail (1 mile). Convenient for commuters with proximity to 267, 495, 66,  Dulles Airport, and metro! Feel like going out? Old Town Herndon and Reston Town Center are minutes away. Wolf Trap, One Loudoun, Arlington, DC, Old Town Leesburg, and Loudoun's winery scene are all within easy driving distance, too. Live your best life in this great home!     [Seller is a Realtor]

Large spacious home in highly desirable Burke Station Square, less than a 1/2 mile from Burke VRE and just minutes from Burke Lake Park. OPEN THIS SUN from 1-4. This gorgeous colonial SFH is beautiful both inside and out. Don't miss the amazing screened in porch looking out to the huge corner lot, which has plenty of play space, yet remains quite private from all the surrounding trees.  Right off the screened-in-porch is a deck with built-in seating and picnic table, perfect for entertaining. There is also a shed and plenty of side space to add-on a garage or car port. As you walk up to one of the larger homes in the community, check out the large front porch, with plenty of seating room. What a great way to enjoy the sites and sounds of the community, not to mention stay up-to-date on all the neighborhood gossip! ;o) As you head inside the home, you are surrounded by great, open living space...and fireplaces! TWO! The first in the the formal dining room that also has beamed ceilings and built-ins surrounding the stone mantle. The other, a brick fireplace in the large, open and bright family room. You can easily access the kitchen, eat-in area and screened-in-porch from the family room. There is also a side service door that leaves right to the driveway area, making unloading groceries very convenient.  There is a bonus room/game room off the kitchen that connects the DR, Kitchen and main level BR/Office. The main level BR is quite large (14x15) and has a huge bay window and built-ins PLUS a 1/2 bath en suite.  Upstairs there are 3 BRs and two full baths, with the primary bath being en suite. Not only is the primary BR huge and bright, but, the secondary BRs are also quite spacious, shiny and bright.  The entire upper floor and basement have all new plush carpet and the main floor has brand new LVP in almost every room.  The basement not only has access to the outside, but also a HUGE rec room, that is just waiting to be made-over with your personal tastes in mind. There is also a great work room with equipments and space to build anything you want...or convert into a playroom or gym. Finally, there is a large layundry/storage area, with plenty of space for all your "stuff,"  So many great features - both inside and out...plus LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION!! welcome HOME!

Wonderfully maintained contemporary colonial build in 2014 by Stanley Martin home features 5BD/4.5BA with airy 10-ft ceilings, upgraded hardwood floors and over 4400 sq. ft. of living space. Upon entering, the spacious foyer sweeps into the bright front room. The open floor plan allows for effortless movement between the formal dining room, family room, and gourmet kitchen. Gather with loved ones around the fireplace in the large family room and host dinner parties with ease! A vast kitchen island anchors the stunning kitchen, which features stainless steel appliances, a deep sink, double ovens, and plenty of cabinet space. A comprehensive kitchen for the most discerning home cook! Convenient half bath off of the kitchen. Upstairs, the palatial primary bedroom features a tray ceiling, enormous walk-in closet, motorized room darkening cellular shades (Bluetooth capable and remote control) and luxurious touches in the ensuite bathroom. Separate vanities frame a deep soaking tub and a coveted rain shower head completes the large shower stall. Upstairs, there is an additional bedroom with a roomy closets and ceiling fan, and a second full bathroom that is bright with plenty of storage. In the lower level of the home, you'll find a rec room, great for additional living options like a home gym or office, and a third bedroom and bathroom. The large laundry room with additional storage can also be found on this level. Walk out onto your deck and picture relaxing and entertaining outside all season long. Stairs lead down into the flat grassy yard. Each bathroom has been renovated with natural stone, porcelain and custom vanities and lighting. New pictures added! Open house, Sunday, Sept 17th. Call to schedule. 

Available for move-in on Sept 23, 2023. 

New vinyl flooring throughout (stairs are currently being installed) and will be freshly painted before move-in. Come and check it out! 

This charming and well maintained 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom townhome is conveniently centered between Fairfax and Centreville on route 29. It's less than two miles from Trader Joe's and Lifetime Fitness; 5 miles from Costco, Wegmans (Fairfax and Chantilly locations), Fairfax County Government Center, Fairfax Corner and Fair Lakes Shopping Mall; 8 miles from George Mason University. The upper level has three spacious bedrooms with high ceilings with fans and plenty of living space and storage space, two full baths on the upper level, and one-half bath on the second level. ***OFFER DEADLINE SATURDAY, AUGUST 26 AT 6 P.M.  Welcome to 6213 Riverland Run!  You are going to love this beautiful colonial by NV Homes (Chapel Hill II model) located in Virginia Run, one of Centreville’s most sought-after neighborhoods.  This 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath, 3714 total sf home (per tax record on Fairfax County site) has a 2-car garage, is situated on 0.3 acres, and backs to woods which provides a peaceful, private retreat at the end of the day.  As you step into the welcoming foyer, you’ll notice the decorative trim and beautiful hardwoods that flow throughout the main level and up the staircase.  To the right is a coat closet, and through a large, cased opening on the left is the formal living room where you’ll find recessed lighting and crown molding.  The living room opens to the light-filled formal dining room featuring more decorative molding and a bay window.  The kitchen is a cook’s dream with custom cabinetry, under-cabinet lighting, center island, large pantry, stainless steel appliances (including double oven and gas cooktop that’s vented to the outside), granite countertops, and tile backsplash.  The breakfast area features another bay window with a view of the backyard.  The family room boasts vaulted ceilings, ceiling fan, gas log fireplace, and a slider out to the expansive deck and flagstone patio—perfect for entertaining.  Rounding out the main level is a mud/laundry room and powder room.  Upstairs you’ll find 4 bedrooms and 2 full, updated baths.  The spacious primary bedroom features vaulted ceilings, ceiling fan, and double doors leading into the lovely en suite with a walk-in closet and luxurious finishes.  There you will find an extra deep soaking tub, double vanities, and a beautifully tiled, oversized shower with frameless door.  Down the hall are the 3 secondary bedrooms with crown molding and ceiling fans, and a hall bath with a shower/tub combo.  On the lower level is a rec room with recessed lighting, full bath, vast storage area, and a walk-out leading to the flagstone patio.  All of the major items have been done, and the home has been meticulously maintained.  Don’t let this one get away!  Roof (2018), Carrier HVAC (2019), water heater (2020), all carpeting (2021), asphalt driveway (2021), deck refinished (2021), hardwoods installed on stairs and in kitchen and all wood floors refinished (2021), flagstone patio (2022), vinyl siding (1999), windows replaced (2003), garage door (2011).  **Updates prior to 2021 based on info from previous owner.

Here's your chance to own a stunning and exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence nestled in the heart of Lorton. Freshly painted 2023, Roof 2011, Fence 2013, Gutters and Electric Panel 2015,  All windows replaced 2016, Hot water heater, Range/Oven, Microwave, Dishwasher replaced 2019, Washer and Dryer 2020,  Kitchen Sink and Faucet 2021, Refrigerator with Ice maker 2022 and Bathroom seats 2023. 2 assigned parking, Spots number 56. Welcome to this magnificent home offering a gracious floorplan with fabulous flow for everyday living and perfect for both casual and formal entertaining! Enjoy pool parties or relax and soak up the sun in the SPARKLING, SALTWATER, IN-GROUND POOL with a waterfall and a diving board allowing 9 ‘of diving pleasure.  You can even unwind after a long day in the attached in-ground spa! The spectacular stone retaining walls & steps, thoughtfully designed lush landscaping with a sprinkler system servicing the entire property, custom outdoor lighting surrounding the pool, and an expansive 2-tier Trex deck create an idyllic outdoor oasis! Upon entrance, you are warmly greeted by the soaring 2-story foyer. Adjacent to the foyer is a private office and a convenient, renovated powder room. Elegant moldings and hardwood floors highlight the formal living and dining rooms, and the dining room features a large bay window bump-out overlooking the picturesque backyard. The heart of the home is the kitchen which offers ample cabinet & counter space, custom tile floor, a center island, and quality appliances. The kitchen flows into the dramatic, 2-story family room featuring a vaulted ceiling and cozy floor-to-ceiling masonry brick fireplace with custom built-in bookcases and mantle. Start your day and enjoy birdwatching in the sunlit breakfast bay which overlooks the backyard & pool. Hummingbirds may even visit you at the window! The laundry room completes the main level floorplan and offers a door to the garage & cabinet space. Hardwood floors extend from the staircase to the upper hall. Upstairs you’ll find spacious bedrooms including the luxury primary suite, complete with a large walk-in closet and beautifully custom remodeled ensuite bathroom with a skylight, soaking tub, and separate shower. The secondary bedrooms are served by a full upper hall bathroom with a skylight & custom vanity with a linen tower. The sizable loft offers closet space, overlooks the family room, and is another great space to work from home! The loft can also be easily closed off for a traditional bedroom. The walkout lower level features a rec room with a second fireplace, a full bathroom, a large den with closet space (could be used as a bedroom), and storage space. The lower level has plenty of room for recreation, gaming, fitness, and more! Located in sought-after, amenity-rich Virginia Run with basketball courts, tennis, pickleball courts, tot lots, pool, community center, and miles of trails. Easy access to commuter routes dining, shopping, and parks. Bring your pool floats, swimming gear and make this house your home!**OVER $175K IN UPDATES INCLUDE:  Driveway*Water heater*Powder room,*Primary bath*HVAC*Pool equipment/replaster/retile*Carpet*Trex Deck*Garage doors...and more! See list of improvements in documents section.

Step into a world of modern elegance with this stunning Colonial home, nestled on a tranquil drive within the highly sought-after Sequoia Farms Community. A picturesque front porch sets the stage for the timeless charm that awaits within. Experience culinary delight in the fully renovated kitchen, featuring pristine white shaker-style cabinetry, sumptuous granite countertops adorned with an exquisite backsplash, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances.  Beautiful tile flooring adds a touch of sophistication to the room. Adjacent to the kitchen, the family room is a haven of relaxation and entertainment. Sunlight streams through expansive windows, highlighting vaulted ceilings, rich wood floors, and a cozy brick fireplace. This inviting space seamlessly connects to the casual dining area and kitchen as well as an expansive deck and patio, overlooking a lush, manicured lawn that affords ample room for various outdoor activities, while a backdrop of majestic trees ensures privacy. To the right of the foyer, you'll find the formal living and dining rooms, adorned with hardwood flooring,  thoughtfully designed to be open and interconnected for effortless hosting of guests. These spaces exude an air of refinement and warmth. Conveniently located in the center hall, a tastefully renovated half bath adds a touch of modern elegance for visiting guests. Ascend to the upper level, where wood flooring continues throughout. An exquisite overlook into the two-story family room adds a unique architectural touch. The primary suite is a spacious sanctuary, complete with custom closet organization and a captivating barn-style sliding door. The primary bath has been fully reimagined, boasting a walk-in shower with seamless glass surround, opulent tiles and fixtures, upscale double vanities, towel warmers, and upgraded  lighting – making it the ultimate pampering retreat. Three additional generously sized bedrooms provide ample closet space and share a fully renovated hall bath adorned with upscale finishes. For movie enthusiasts, the lower level offers a perfect escape. A tastefully finished recreation room is equipped with a flat screen, sconces for dimmable lighting, while a designated zone awaits for exercise or office needs. An additional renovated full bath with fine finishes adds convenience, along with a storage room housing a washer, dryer, and utility sink. As an unexpected bonus, a sauna awaits to provide the ultimate in relaxation at the end of a long day. A roomy two car garage finishes off this great home. This home is the epitome of turnkey perfection, ready to welcome its fortunate new owners into a world of elegance and comfort.

Welcome to SummerHill neighborhood! Amazing Opportunity to Own this Little Paradise in Lorton. Beautifully Maintained Corner Lot SF Home offers 3 beds and 2.5 baths. Upgraded Top to Bottom. New HVAC and Water Heater. Newer Roof. Walk-in to the house with Open Kitchen Concept with Luxury Ceramic tiles. Heated Kitchen Floors. Newer Kitchen Cabinets and Newer SS Appliances. Pebbles around the bird bath are from Imperial beach which makes it Unique.  Fresh Smell of Jasmine and Honeysuckle will relax you while sitting at the porch in evening. Gas Pool Heating system. Full Size Shed in the back. 2nd Concrete porch next to pool so you have invite more friend and enjoy your summer afternoons. Location and convenience!! Shopping, parks and trails, restaurants, schools, and easy access to Fort Belvoir & Quantico and Major Highways (I495 and Route 1). Its a Must See!!! It Won't Last Long!!!

Immaculate and light brick front colonial in popular Sully Station!  Four bedrooms, 2.5 baths.  Open two story foyer. Hardwood floors on main level. Library/office with attractive built-ins.
