Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a tranquil and convenient neighborhood!  This immaculate property boasts an array of fantastic upgrades and modern amenities that promise a comfortable and stylish living experience. Step inside and be greeted by the spacious living room featuring a charming window seat, perfect for enjoying natural light and relaxing moments. Discover the joy of culinary delights in the all-new kitchen, which was thoughtfully renovated in 2022. This modern kitchen boasts ceiling-height shaker-style soft-close cabinets, granite counters, a deep apron-front sink, and plenty of lower drawers for added convenience. The upper floor houses all three bedrooms, an en suite bathroom and an additional full bath, while the main level features a half bath strategically located just inside the entryway for guests. Indulge in the lap of luxury in the newly renovated primary bathroom featuring a custom-tiled walk-in shower, ensuring you start and end your day in style. The main bathroom and powder room have been tastefully updated, further adding to the charm of this home. The attention to detail is evident throughout, with all-new light fixtures and fans installed in 2020,  brand-new oak stairs and modern railings added in 2021,  a new roof, windows, insulated garage door, blinds and shades all replaced in November 2019. The home's interior has been freshly painted, adding a touch of sophistication and modernity. Beyond the walls, you'll find a serene neighborhood with access to nature trails right behind the community. Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to own a thoughtfully upgraded and perfectly located property. Schedule your visit today and be prepared to fall in love with this truly special home!

Step into the gourmet kitchen, complete with a gas stove, sleek granite countertops, and gleaming stainless steel appliances. The formal dining room boasts elegant chair rail detail, setting the stage for memorable gatherings. Cozy up in the living room by the warm glow of the gas fireplace, perfect for relaxing evenings. Exquisite, brick-front estate home with nearly 7,000 square feet of finished living space, situated on 1.25 grassy acres in the desired Occoquan Overlook community. This is luxury living at its finest! Enter the bright front foyer, flanked by the formal living and dining rooms, accented by arched doorways, crown molding, chair rail with picture and decorative trim work. Hardwood floors guide you through the main level, starting in the living room and into the light-filled sunroom--the perfect place to snuggle up with a book or take a nap. The private library features floor to ceiling built-ins and windows, overlooking the trees. The rear foyer opens to the elevated deck, ready for summer grilling and watching the fireflies.  Step through to the family room with 3-sides of windows and a stone-face gas fireplace. The family room is open to the kitchen--updated with stainless steel GE Monogram appliances, granite countertops, and modern hood fan. The large custom-color island offers extra seating and the prep space your inner-chef craves. The walk-in pantry provides plenty of space for all your kitchen gadgets, and the secondary entry makes unloading your Costco haul a breeze and keeps the crew's stuff out of sight!  Move the party downstairs to the expansive lower level rec room. With a wet bar and full size refrigerator, you can craft cocktails while the crew hangs out. The French door opens to a paver patio and into the grassy yard. Roll into the theater room, with dramatic paint and custom "screen" on the wall. Whether it's the newest Mission Impossible thriller or the big sportsball game, you'll feel like you're part of the action! Bonus room in the rear includes a large window to view the movie screen--great for a home gym or hobby space. The large bonus room off the main area has access to the fourth full bathroom, and can be used as guest space, play room, storage--use your imagination! Ready to wind down? Head upstairs to the serene primary suite. Escape the hustle and bustle of the everyday to your own haven! The bedroom has a dramatic vaulted ceiling and overlooks the trees. A 3-sided glass fireplace divides the sleeping and sitting areas, and access to not one, not two, but THREE walk-in closets, each with custom organizers and shelving! The large private bath has dual vanities, walk-in shower, private water closet, and luxurious jetted tub. Bring your own bubble bath! Down the hall is the spacious bedroom 2 with a private ensuite bath and walk-in closet. Bedrooms 3 and 4 share a Jack-and-Jill style bathroom with dual vanity. Don't miss the ultimate convenience--the laundry room with extra storage on the bedroom level! Throughout the home you will find recessed lighting, whole-home speaker system, and beautiful architectural details.  The 3-car garage offers space for your everyday vehicles, as well as those for weekend fun--kayaks, bicycles, ATVs, you name it! This quiet community is tucked into the heart of Northern Virginia, with easy access to the major commuter routes 123, FC Parkway and I-95. There's so much to enjoy in this area, including Historic Occoquan, the Workhouse Arts Center, Fountainhead Regional Park, Burke Lake Park and other trails. Come visit and make this your new home sweet home!

This beautiful Stanley Martin Taylor model house is located in a quiet, secluded area of Centreville, VA. It's nestled on a generous half-acre, and feeds into highly-rated Loudoun County schools. The home itself is spacious and well-appointed, with plenty of room for entertaining and relaxing. This 5 bed/4.5 bath 4-story single family house includes a morning room, a loft with terrace, a two-car and a single-car garage, a water filtration and softener system, and unfinished space for another bed/bath and basement area. The main level of the home features a living room, formal dining room, and a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The kitchen opens up to a morning room and spacious family room with a fireplace and coffered ceilings. There is one bedroom, one half bath, and one full bath on the main level.  Upstairs, there are four bedrooms, three full baths, and the laundry. The master bedroom has its own private bathroom and two walk-in closets. One bedroom has its own bath and walk-in closet.  One more level up, there is also a loft with a walk-out balcony overlooking a peaceful wooded area. The walk-out basement is semi-finished with room to build another bedroom, full bathroom, and media room. The property also has a lot of flat land, perfect for a garden, playground, or pets. Colonial by design with a fun contemporary flair! Open bright main level flows easily from room to room. The spacious Living Room leads to a large Dining Room. Both rooms offer excellent floor space for formal gatherings or more casual get-togethers. Newer roof,  gutters, hot water heater, remodeled kitchen, remodeled bathrooms, replacement windows/sliding doors, trex deck, paver patio, hardwood floors, mutiple fireplaces,  decorative moldings/wood work,  and a fenced yard are just some of the fine features that make this home so desireable! Surrounded by  parks, this enchanting 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home offers a convenience in commute and, at the end of the day, a serene place to come home to and enjoy.  Hardwood flooring in the foyer welcomes you home and ushers you into the bright and spacious living room on the left where twin windows stream natural light. The adjoining dining room offers plenty of space for all occasions, as chair rail and a frosted-glass chandelier with ceiling medallion add a distinctly refined flair. The remodeled gourmet kitchen stirs the senses with gleaming granite countertops, 42 inch cabinets, and stainless steel appliances including a gas range and French door refrigerator. Enjoy morning coffee at the center island's breakfast bar, in the adjoining breakfast area, or step outside to the trex deck with descending stairs to the custom designed patio with half sitting wall, verdant lawn,  and post and rail fencing—seamlessly blending indoor and outdoor dining and entertaining. Back inside, relax and unwind in the family room where a soaring vaulted ceiling plays up the light from twin skylights and a wood burning fireplace with wood mantel serves as the focal point of the room, a home office,  a laundry room, and powder room add convenience and round out the main level.  Upstairs, the spacious primary suite offers  a walk-in closet tailored with custom shelving, and a remodeled luxurious ensuite bath boasting a dual-sink vanity, sumptuous vessel soaking tub, frameless ultra shower, and sparkling spa-toned tile flooring and surround—the finest in personal pampering! Down the hall, three additional bright and spacious bedrooms, each with lighted ceiling fans and generous closet space, enjoy easy access to the beautifully appointed hall bath. Fine craftsmanship continues in the lower level recreation room highlighted by separate areas for media, games, or simple relaxation and is highlighted by a second gas fireplace and a pub-style wet bar that is sure to be a popular destination for family and friends; as two versatile bonus rooms plus additional full bath and ample storage solutions complete the comfort and luxury of this wonderful home.  Loaded with amenities, Virginia Run offers  an outdoor pool, community center,  pickleball courts, tennis courts, basketball courts, tot lots,  and miles of jogging/walking paths. Commuters will appreciate the close proximity to I-66, Express Lanes, Routes 28 and 29, Fairfax County Parkway, and other major routes. Plenty of diverse and trendy shopping, dining, and entertainment choices are available throughout the area including Fair Lakes Shopping Center and Fair Oaks Mall and outdoor enthusiasts will enjoy exploring nearby parks. For a retreat that offers sophistication and comfort, you’ve found it. Welcome home!

This spacious , brick front, 3 level single family home sits on generous 1/3 + acre , leveled lot in  friendly and amenity rich Virginia Run Community. Almost 3400 sq ft of taxable finished area on Main and Upper levels.  PLEASE CHECK THE 3D TOUR . As you walk into the home, you are greeted with warmth and light in a 2 story foyer. Hardwood on all of the main level , stairs and  upper level hallway . Your Living and formal Dining rooms are right and left as you enter with elegant chair railing and moldings. Formal Dining room leads to a large gourmet kitchen, with granite counter tops / backsplash and stainless-steel appliances. New refrigerator with French doors, ice maker and bottom freezer. New down draft cooktop. New disposer and newer dishwasher. Built in Microwave and oven. Pantry with swing door shelves . Kitchen flows seamlessly to a relaxing and generous breakfast area with light from many directions.  French doors open to the flat backyard. 2 story vaulted ceiling   Family room with a fire place and plenty of light from windows and skylights. Work from home from the  office room that has a beautiful bay window that gives a relaxing view of the green backyard.. Upper level boasts a primary bedroom with generous “His “and “Hers” separate Walk-in closets. Primary bath updated with new tile flooring, 2 sink vanity with granite counter top and new lighting fixtures. Hardwood hallway with 2 sky lights leads to bedrooms 2,3 , 4 and laundry room . Hallway bathroom updated with new tile flooring, 2 sink vanity with granite counter tops and lighting fixtures. Great location , just one block from Rec Center and community pool, tot lots and Tennis courts. Miles of walking and biking trails. Close to Cub Run stream.  A short distance to Virginia Run Elementary school and only a few Miles to Dulles Int. Airport. Commuters paradise ; close to shopping, I66, R28, R29 and Metro Park and Ride.

This beautiful home sits on a gorgeous 1/2++ACRE (.64) FLAT OPEN LOT with privacy trees backing to the JMRC recreational center and not often seen in Virginia Run.  Have your own soccer game in your backyard!  LOTS TO LOVE INSIDE AND OUT of this home; from its fantastic yard, striking brick front facade, and side-load garage exterior to the interior loaded with large open flowing rooms and modern touches throughout its three levels of almost 3,400 finished square feet.  BRAND NEW PLUSH CARPET ON UPPER LEVEL and 2 staircases plus basement and bedroom 2 freshly painted. Tall windows throughout welcome the natural light and enhance the main level REAL hardwood floors.  Modernized kitchen with center island breakfast bar opens to the bright breakfast area and family room set under a vaulted ceiling. The Family Room enjoys a soaring brick hearth flanked by windows. The FRESHLY PAINTED SUN DECK welcomes relaxation while that huge lot welcomes all the fun and games! The primary bedroom enjoys excellent floor space to accommodate a sitting nook, plus has an extra deep walk-in closet, and en-suite bath with a double sink vanity and separate soaking tub.  Downstairs, the extensive full basement, with a full bath and egress window, has an open L-shaped recreation area for a multitude of activities: TV/media, games, exercise, and much more. Be sure to check out the MASSIVE STORAGE AREA too! The VIRGINIA RUN community offers on-site recreation amenities (clubhouse with pool, various sport courts, playgrounds, and walking trails. In fact, the Cub Run Valley Stream Park borders the west side of the community with miles of walking/biking trails meandering through woods, open pastoral space, and crisscrossing the Cub Run stream.   Such a convenient location - a short walk to Va Run Elementary and JMRC Rec Center!  Move in and enjoy!

Welcome to Country Club Manor, this is an established family friendly neighborhood with walking trails, REC pool, tennis courts and a Country Club nearby. NO HOA! This updated home offers 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms. A wonderful open concept kitchen, dining room, and living room area with a cozy fireplace to keep your family close. The lower level has a full bath and bedroom for guests or an office, the family room is perfect for recreation, there is extra space for a gym or additional play area for the kids. Enjoy the outdoors in your screened-in porch or the spacious backyard that is fully fenced. This home is centrally located to highways (I66 & RT 28), commuter routes, shopping, entertainment, dining and much more. Don't miss this great opportunity!    Recent upgrades include new kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops. Please review ShowingTime request instructions.  Accepting Back up Offers

This stunning home sits on a quiet cul de sac street in sought-after, amenity-rich Virginia Run! The gracious, well-appointed floor plan has plenty of space for any occasion. Sun cascades through the open main level floorplan. The welcoming foyer invites you into this gracious home and the center hall features a convenient powder room with a quartz-top vanity. The heart of the home is the custom-renovated gourmet kitchen which boasts quartz counters, a center island, custom cherry cabinetry w/42-inch cabinets, soft close drawers & pantry cabinets, under cabinet lights, recessed lighting, stylish tile backsplash, and quality stainless steel appliances including a GE Café, flat surface range w/convection oven, GE built-in microwave, GE French door refrigerator with bottom freezer, wall mounted range hood, and a Bosch dishwasher. The kitchen flows into the dramatic, sunlit family room with a ceiling fan, a cozy fireplace, and a door to the deck. Relax and unwind after a long day or enjoy summer barbecues on the rear deck with a pergola, built-in seating, and steps down to the large, level, fenced backyard. Start your day in the sunny breakfast room overlooking the backyard! The formal living and dining rooms adjacent to the foyer feature crisp, elegant moldings. Hardwood floors extend throughout the entire main level. The upper level offers carpet with plush, updated padding, and 4 bedrooms including the spacious primary suite featuring an updated ensuite bathroom with tile flooring, a walk-in closet, and a double vanity with granite countertop and a make-up counter. The second, third, and fourth bedrooms are served by a full dual-entry hall bathroom with a double bowl vanity and access from both the hall and the second bedroom. In the finished basement, you'll find low maintenance engineered hardwood floors, an expansive rec room (pool table and entertainment center convey!), a wet bar with cabinet space, and a third full bathroom. The lower level also offers a storage area, a front-load washer & dryer, and a utility sink. Other features include Soft-lite triple pane windows with argon fill, a whole-house humidifier, updated insulated garage doors, an updated water heater, a new clothes washer, new exterior paint, extra attic insulation & more!  Community basketball courts, tennis, pickleball courts, tot lots, a pool, a community center, and miles of trails. Easy access to commuter routes, dining, shopping, parks, & more!

Lovely home with the prime location! 5 minutes to Centreville and all the favorite food options - have you tried Sweet Rolled Tacos Ice Cream?! Also a little known gem of a Coast Guard Exchange there.  15 minutes drive to Fairfax for all the essentials and enjoyment offered there.  And your new home sweet home?  It backs up to trees so you can enjoy your morning coffee or evening drinks with friends in quiet and privacy on your back floating deck.  Step inside and kick off your shoes before unwinding or continuing to work in the living room, or cooking up a meal in the kitchen at the heart of the home.  Separate dining room is sunny, with the convenience of a pass through ledge to the kitchen or sliding glass doors out for grilling.  Let's be honest, everyone needs a ledge to collect the keys and mail though.   Don't miss the powder room off the living room also. The upstairs provides for everything else - sleeping, working, laundry and storage!  Stacked washer and dryer might help you get that clean laundry folded sooner than if you had to trudge down to a basement.  Three bedrooms and two baths to choose from,  all with plenty of closets but you also have pull down stairs to an attic you can load up with decorations and luggage.   Everything you need and want is move in ready!
